# Progress — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/progress.css`

## Architecture

ALL styling in CSS via `@apply` + raw CSS. React only composes class names via `clsx`. Presentational.

## CSS Classes

### Base
`.acko-progress` — `@apply w-full`

### Label
- `.acko-progress-label-wrapper` — `@apply flex justify-between`, margin-bottom `--space-1`
- `.acko-progress-label` — `--font-caption-size`, color `--color-text-muted`

### Track
- `.acko-progress-track` — `@apply w-full rounded-full overflow-hidden`, bg `--color-border-subtle`
- `.acko-progress-track-sm` — height `--scale-4`
- `.acko-progress-track-md` — height `--scale-8`
- `.acko-progress-track-lg` — height `--scale-12`

### Bar
- `.acko-progress-bar` — `@apply h-full rounded-full`, transition width 500ms `--ease-out-cubic`
- `.acko-progress-bar-primary/success/error` — fills with respective `--color-*` token

### Animated
- `.acko-progress-animated` — adds shimmer keyframe to bar
